{"tid":1563442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"制裁地鐵免費報章正展開展","createTime":"2019-09-12T11:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T11:57:09.000Z","uid":267263,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1b62115442407848285749b134d09a6adc73db26","tid":1563442,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"極紅<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">頭條日報</span></strong>每日喺黨鐵派成幾十萬份,呃人老母,係文宣第二大公敵<br />\n<br />\n制裁頭條日報比制裁TVB仲簡單<br />\n<br />\n由聽日開始,每人經過黨鐵就拎一份,轉過頭就抌咗佢(廢紙回收箱)<br />\n<br />\n記住<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你每拎一份就少一個老母比人呃</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KJqERvU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKJqERvU.jpg&h=e783e6f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Khcr4g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Khcr4g.jpg&h=e0c912c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KugTVXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKugTVXD.jpg&h=b81e4504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X12jRv0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX12jRv0.jpg&h=6aff8ca9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cde0da8ef92d3a4a1d6ea276e3b7169cec3b6a9","tid":1563442,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:47:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><